// Semantic direction:
// parallell_bfs expands the frontier level by level using all available threads.
// pbfs_bottomup scans all unvisited vertices checking if any neighbor is in the frontier.
// pbfs_hybridretning switches between top-down and bottom-up based on frontier density.
// pbfs_atomisk_visited uses atomic compare-and-swap to mark vertices as visited safely.
// psssp_delta_stepping groups vertices into bøtter by distance mod delta_verdi.
// lett_kant has weight ≤ delta_verdi; tung_kant has weight > delta_verdi.
// psssp_tøm_bøtte processes all vertices in the lowest non-empty bucket in parallel.
// pscc_dcsc (Divide-and-Conquer SCC) recursively finds SCCs using forward/backward BFS.
// pscc_fwbw is the parallel FW-BW algorithm: BFS from pivot forward and backward simultaneously.
// pmst_filter_kruskal randomly samples edges and filters those connecting same-component vertices.
// graphblas expresses graph algorithms as linear algebra over user-defined semirings.
// gb_mxv (matrix-vector product) implements BFS, SSSP, and PageRank as matrix operations.
// gb_semiring replaces standard (plus, times) with custom (min, plus) for shortest paths.
// pregel_modell is the vertex-centric BSP model: think-like-a-vertex, communicate via messages.
// pregel_superstep synchronizes all vertices before the next round of message passing.
// ligra is a shared-memory framework with edgeMap/vertexMap primitives for graph algorithms.
// gunrock_gpu implements frontier-based graph traversal on GPUs with load-balanced expansion.

// Primitive flow:
// parallell BFS hybrid: if |grense| > β*|V|: bottomup else: topdown
//   topdown: for hvert v i grense (parallellt): for nabo w: atomisk mark w -> neste_grense
//   bottomup: for hvert ubesøkt v (parallellt): hvis nabo i grense -> mark v -> neste_grense
// delta-stepping SSSP: initialisér bøtte[0] = {kilde}
//   while bøtter ikke tomme: ta ut laveste bøtte
//     parallellt: slapp av alle lett_kant -> oppdater bøtter
//     etterarbeid: slapp av alle tung_kant fra tømt bøtte
// GraphBLAS BFS: v = initiell_grense (mask-vektor)
//   repeat: v_ny = A' mxv v (over bool semiring) AND NOT besøkt
//   oppdater besøkt -> gjenta til v_ny tom
// Pregel PageRank: superstep 0: send PR/grad til naboer
//   superstep t: for hvert vertex: PR_ny = (1-d)/N + d*Σ(mottatte meldinger)
//   send PR_ny/grad videre -> gjenta til konvergens

// This defines parallel graph algorithms: hybrid top-down/bottom-up BFS, delta-stepping SSSP,
// DC-SCC with forward/backward BFS, parallel Borůvka MST, GraphBLAS linear algebra model,
// Pregel vertex-centric BSP, Ligra shared-memory framework, and GPU graph traversal.

// ---- from runtime/z570.no ----
