// Semantic direction:
// planargraf is a graph that can be embedded in the plane without edge crossings.
// kuratowski_teorem: a graph is planar iff it contains no subdivision of K₅ or K₃,₃.
// boyer_myrvold is an O(n) planarity test that produces either an embedding or a Kuratowski subgraph.
// lr_planarity (Left-Right Planarity) tests planarity via orientation of back edges.
// dcel_datastruktur (Doubly-Connected Edge List) represents planar embeddings efficiently.
// halfkant_tvilling is the reverse direction of a directed half-edge.
// halfkant_ansikt gives the face to the left of a directed half-edge.
// euler_V_E_F: V - E + F = 2 for connected planar graphs; gives maximum edge bounds.
// schnyder_woods decomposes a triangulated planar graph into three spanning trees.
// fary_teorem guarantees every planar graph has a straight-line embedding.
// tutte_embedding places inner vertices at the barycenter of their neighbors for convex faces.
// fire_farge_teorem: every planar graph is 4-colorable.
// fire_farging_lineær produces a 4-coloring in O(n²) using the Appel-Haken proof structure.
// grötzsch_teorem: every triangle-free planar graph is 3-colorable.
// planar_separator_teorem: every planar graph has a separator of size O(√n).
// lipton_tarjan finds the separator by finding a BFS tree and selecting the right level.
// sssp_plan_linear computes SSSP in planar graphs in O(n) using the FR algorithm.
// succinkt_representasjon encodes planar graphs in O(n) bits while supporting adjacency queries.

// Primitive flow:
// Boyer-Myrvold planarity: DFS -> numerér noder -> for hvert edge: klassifisér som tree/back
//   bygg biconnected components -> test LR-orientering for hvert komponent
//   feil: finn Kuratowski subgraf -> returner sertifikat
// Tutte embedding: velg ytre ansikt som trekant
//   fikser ytre vertices -> sett indre vertices som gjennomsnitt av naboer
//   løs lineært system (Laplacian) -> konveks tegning
// Planar separator: BFS fra vilkårlig kilde -> finn nivå l med |nivå l| ≤ √n
//   separator = nivå l ∪ nivå l-√n -> deler graf i to deler ≤ 2n/3
// Fire-farging greedy med hjelp av planarttest:
//   fire_farge_teorem garanterer eksistens -> iterativ farge med 4 farger via Kempe-kjeder

// This defines planar graph algorithms: Boyer-Myrvold/LR planarity testing, DCEL embedding,
// Euler's formula consequences, Schnyder woods, Tutte embedding, four-color theorem, planar
// separator theorem, linear-time SSSP, and succinct planar graph encoding.

