// Semantic direction:
// infinity_kategori (∞,1)-category has morphisms at all levels; 1-morphisms are the interesting ones.
// homotopi_kategori is obtained by identifying homotopic morphisms — the shadow of an ∞-category.
// modelkategori provides an abstract framework for doing homotopy theory in any category.
// svak_ekvivalens generalizes homotopy equivalence; not necessarily iso but becomes iso in Ho(C).
// fibrasjon_mk is a map with the right lifting property against acyclic cofibrations.
// kofibrasjon_mk is a map with the left lifting property against acyclic fibrations.
// løft_aksiomet: given a commutative square with a cofibration and fibration, a lift exists.
// quillen_ekvivalens induces an equivalence of homotopy categories.
// quasikategori (Joyal model) is a simplicial set where all inner horns can be filled.
// kan_fibrasjon fills ALL horns; quasicategories fill only INNER horns.
// lurie_framework: Higher Topos Theory and Higher Algebra extend classical results to ∞-categories.
// stable_infinity_kategori has finite limits and colimits, with the loop-suspension adjunction as an equivalence.
// spectrum is the stabilization of spaces; represents generalized cohomology theories.
// presentable_kategorier are accessible with small colimits — the right notion for ∞-toposes.
// deriverte_kategorier are the classical precursors to stable ∞-categories.
// motivisk_homotopi applies homotopy theory to algebraic geometry (Morel-Voevodsky).
// kondensert_matematik (Clausen-Scholze) provides solid foundations for analytic geometry.

// Primitive flow:
// Modelkategori-faktorisering: for f: A → B
//   faktorisér f = pi ∘ i: A → C → B
//   i er kofibrasjon+svak_ekvivalens (acyclic cofibration)
//   pi er fibrasjon (og vice versa)
// Quillen derived functor: F: C → D venstre_quillen
//   LF(X) = F(QX) der QX er kofibrant erstatning av X
//   LF er universell mellom F og funktorene som inverterer svak_ekvivalenser
// Quasikategori komposisjon: f: X→Y, g: Y→Z
//   velg fyllning av inner horn Λ¹₂ → Δ² -> komposisjon h: X→Z
//   komposisjon er unik opp til contractibel valg (ikke på nesen)
// Spectral sequence: filtrasjon av kompleks → E₂ side →...→ E∞ side konvergerer til H*(X)

// This defines ∞-category theory: model categories with Quillen adjunctions, quasi-categories
// (Joyal/Lurie), stable ∞-categories and spectra, presentable categories, motivic homotopy
// theory, derived categories, and condensed mathematics.

